<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact - OWCS Tipping</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/global.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/interactive.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/match-cards.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/info.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Contact</h1>
        <p>
          Get in touch regarding site issues, questions, or feedback.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container info-layout">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>General Enquiries</h2>
          <p>
            If you would like to reach out to me for any reason, please feel free to send me an email at: support@owcstipping.com
          </p>
          <p>
            I would love to hear your feedback, suggestions for improvments, or anything in between.
          </p>
          <p>
            For a more community centered contact platform, there is also a discord server for this site. If you love the community,
            or have things to say, feel free to join the discord and let me know. Discord: https://discord.gg/YpncvpWxhz
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>Bug Reports</h2>
          <p>
            If you encounter any bugs, I encourage you to let me know as i strive for this website to be as user friendly as possible.
            You can submit bug reports through the discord server above, or by emailing me, with the email also shown above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>